                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18161204-91-off494 t18161204-91-cd495"></join>, twenty pounds weight of leather, value 30s.; and one sack, value 2s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18161204-91-victim710" type="victimName">
                     Edward 
